article.description: — Damiree Burns scored 18 points and grabbed 13 rebounds to help Youngstown State defeat Robert Morris 71-57 on Saturday.
article.headline: Burns scores 18, Youngstown State knocks off Robert Morris 71-57
article.linkText: Burns scores 18, Youngstown State knocks off Robert Morris 71-57
article.story: MOON TOWNSHIP, Pa. -- — Damiree Burns scored 18 points and grabbed 13 rebounds to help Youngstown State defeat Robert Morris 71-57 on Saturday. Brett Thompson scored 17 and added six rebounds for the Penguins (5-3). Ziggy Reid finished with 14 points and eight rebounds. The Colonials (2-6) were led by Stephaun Walker, who recorded 20 points and nine rebounds. Robert Morris also got 15 points from Markeese Hastings and 10 points from Justice Williams. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
